name: Welcome to the World of Mibesto803

metadata.name: Mysterious Woman
metadata.description:
She doesn’t talk much about herself, which makes you want to know her even more. She doesn’t care what others do or say nor does she talk about others much. She is calm and quiet, yet questioning and observant. She makes good decisions and she makes them confidently and easily. She picks up on the things you are afraid to voice. 	She loves spending time alone. She is intelligent. She builds close relationships with only a few. This makes you want to be one of them. You may never be able to figure her out, but you intend to keep trying.

Mysterious Woman is Mibesto803’s first NFT minted on his own smart contract.
